xtext.objectsModel

Interface WorkItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregationNode, AnalysisActivity, DevTask, ResolutionActivity, Task, WorkItemEntity, WorkItemImpl

    public interface WorkItem
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Work Item'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Id
    • Description
    • Type
    • Has Predecessors
    • Pd Tasks
    • Sc Tasks
    • Is Aggregation Node
    • Sb Tasks
    • Up Tasks
    • Has Impacts
    • Impacts
    • Required Services
    • Value
    • Arrival Time
    • Due Date

    See Also:
    ObjectsModelPackage.getWorkItem()
